snippet: Israel's U.N. ambassador on Monday denounced a U.N. agency head for tacitly comparing the Jewish state to Nazi Germany and has demanded her suspension....

headline.print_headline: Israel Irked by Diplomat's Tacit Nazi Remark
headline.main: Israel Irked by Diplomat's Tacit Nazi Remark

lead_paragraph: Israel's U.N. ambassador on Monday denounced a U.N. agency head for tacitly comparing the Jewish state to Nazi Germany and has demanded her suspension.
